WEBVTT

11:35.700 --> 11:36.940 line:80%
The restaurant is so lively—

11:36.940 --> 11:38.180 line:80%
it's all thanks to you.

11:38.180 --> 11:39.870 line:80%
What do you mean, thanks to me?

11:39.940 --> 11:42.100 line:80%
Ever since your husband came by,

11:42.100 --> 11:44.360 line:80%
that Qi fellow hasn't bothered me again.

11:44.890 --> 11:46.610 line:80%
I can finally focus on
running the business.
